    <!-- Visualization & Content Choices: 1. Problem Gateway -> Interactive Cards -> Goal: Guide/Empathize -> Justification: Allows users to self-select their primary pain point, making the experience immediately relevant. 2. Founders' Pledge -> Storytelling block -> Goal: Build deep trust -> Justification: Transforms the founders' past struggles into the company's greatest strength and unique selling proposition. 3. Media Brands -> Content Showcase -> Goal: Prove ongoing diligence -> Justification: Positions the content not as self-promotion, but as evidence of continuous, proactive problem-solving on behalf of clients. -->
